business_data.summary: MìLà is a frozen food company specializing in authentic Chinese dumplings, noodles, and sauces, founded by Jen Liao and Caleb Wang in 2018. The company aims to bring restaurant-quality Chinese cuisine to homes across the United States, offering a variety of products including soup dumplings, potstickers, and vegan options. MìLà prides itself on using high-quality, locally sourced ingredients and provides a melt-free guarantee for its frozen products. Customers can shop online with free shipping on orders over $99 and explore various bundles and subscription options for regular deliveries.
